Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
deleteAllFPObjects(25.10)                            deleteAllFPObjects(25.10)

Name
       deleteAllFPObjects - Removes all floorplan objects

Syntax
       deleteAllFPObjects

       [-help]

       Removes  all  floorplan objects. The density screen, obstruction, power
       strips, and route guides objects are  deleted.  The  guides  and  block
       guides  are  cleared from the design area. The physical instance groups
       are also cleared from the core area. Use this command  after  importing
       the design.

Parameters
       -help  Outputs  a  brief description of the deleteAllFPObjects command.
              For a detailed description of the command, use the man  command:
              man deleteAllFPObjects

Related Information
              *
                 deleteSelectedFromFPlan

              * Floorplanning the Design chapter in the Innovus User Guide

              * Floorplan Menu chapter in the Innovus Menu Reference

                * Clear Floorplan

